                <fr:addr type="user">jms-00LM</fr:addr>
                <fr:route>jms-00LM.xml</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="The indicator function of a subset">The indicator function of a subset</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>The <fr:em><fr:strong>indicator function</fr:strong></fr:em> or <fr:em><fr:strong>characteristic function</fr:strong></fr:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> is defined to be the <fr:link href="jms-00LO.xml" title="Predicate" addr="jms-00LO" type="local">predicate</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _S\colon  A\to  {\mathopen {}\left  [2\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> defined piecewise below:</fr:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 \chi _S{\mathopen {}\left (a\right )\mathclose {}} = \begin {cases}
  1 & \text {if } a \in  S\\
  0 & \text {if } a \not \in  S
 \end {cases}
]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2024</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>1</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>25</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:anchor>1874</fr:anchor>
                <fr:addr type="user">jms-00LP</fr:addr>
                <fr:route>jms-00LP.xml</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="The comprehension of a predicate">The comprehension of a <fr:link href="jms-00LO.xml" title="Predicate" addr="jms-00LO" type="local">predicate</fr:link></fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\phi \colon  A\to  {\mathopen {}\left  [2\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="jms-00LO.xml" title="Predicate" addr="jms-00LO" type="local">predicate</fr:link> on a set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>. The <fr:em><fr:strong>comprehension</fr:strong></fr:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\phi ]]></fr:tex> is defined to be the following subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left  [\phi \right  ]\mathclose {}}\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> spanned by elements at which <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\phi ]]></fr:tex> holds, as specified below:</fr:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 {\mathopen {}\left  [\phi \right  ]\mathclose {}} = {\mathopen {}\left \{a\in  A\,\middle \vert \,\phi {\mathopen {}\left (a\right )\mathclose {}}=1\right \}\mathclose {}}
]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
